Add sound support to the RK3066 HDMI driver.
The HDMI TX audio source is connected to I2S_8CH.

Signed-off-by: Zheng Yang <zhengyang@rock-chips.com>
Signed-off-by: Johan Jonker <jbx6244@gmail.com>
